bilingual.source: My brother Said bought me the latest version of that computer program.
bilingual.target: 我哥哥赛义德给我买了那个电脑程序的最新版本。

bilingual.source: This version has a significant unlikeness to the previous one.
bilingual.target: 这个版本和之前的版本有很大的不像。

bilingual.source: This version of the software supersedes all previous versions.
bilingual.target: 这个版本的软件取代了所有以前的版本。

bilingual.source: This version of the game is simpler.
bilingual.target: 这个版本的游戏更简单。

bilingual.source: The new software replaces the old version.
The software version needs to be updated.
bilingual.target: 该软件的版本需要更新。

bilingual.source: This phone comes in a champagne version.
bilingual.target: 这款手机有香槟色的版本。

bilingual.source: This is the latest version of the document.
bilingual.target: 这是该文件的最新版本。

bilingual.source: I like the original version of this song.
bilingual.target: 我喜欢这首歌的原始版本。

yingyinNormal.en: That is now the official version, the version anyone we want to will see.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是官方版本了，其他人所看到的就会是这个版本。

yingyinNormal.en: There's my version of the song. You see? Right there, that's my version, and that is Tiller's.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我的版本的歌曲，看到了吗？在这里，那是我的版本，那是蒂勒的。

yingyinNormal.en: You have your version. I have mine. I'm sure mine will get just as much traction as this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有你的版本，我也有我的，我相信我的版本会跟这个一样引人注目。

yingyinNormal.en: This is going to literally blow your head off and I think my version is actually quite light compared to the real authentic version from Sichuan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它真的能让你脑袋冒烟，我改良的版本比四川正宗的火锅温柔多了。

yingyinNormal.en: But my version wins because it's the better story, and it's also exactly how things went down.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是我的版本会赢，因为这样报道更有意思，并且事情也确实如此。

yingyinNormal.en: And this is my version, and you can tone it down, you know, or have it spicy, or not as spicy as you want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我改良的版本，你可以按照你的喜好进行调整，加辣或是变清淡。

yingyinNormal.en: We need a strong Senate version first, so we don't have two weak bills going into reconciliation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们首先需要一份强势的参议院版本，这样才能避免两部无力的法案相互调和。

yingyinNormal.en: I learned that while most everyone expects the future to be a slightly modified version of the present, it is typically very different.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也明白了虽然每个人觉得未来只是稍有不同的现在版本，但事实是非常不同的。

yingyinNormal.en: So, one of my favorite video games of all time is called Shadow of the Colossus, and it was only for PlayStation 2, but then they came out with a new version for PS3 with better graphics.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最爱的电子游戏之一叫做《汪达与巨像》，是PS2独占游戏，但是后来他们为PS3提供了画质更好的新版本。

yingyinNormal.en: See, Arnold built a version of that cognition in which the hosts heard their programming as an inner monologue, with the hopes that in time, their own voice would take over.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿诺德创建了一份这种版本的认知接待员，可以直接听到对他们的编程，就像是内心独白，希望在将来他们自身的声音会取而代之。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, most of being a parent isn't fair. Right now, Alex is obsessed with some CEO business woman author who's basically an older-looking version of me. We're the same age, by the way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为人父母大部分时候都没有公平可言。现在艾丽克斯迷上了一个什么CEO商业女强人作家，她基本上就是个看起来老一点版本的我。顺带一提我和她同龄。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't want a version. I want a vision.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不要折中，我要大展宏图。

yingyinNormal.en: This is my fresh modern version of that peasant dish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是我的现代版的农民餐。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, and in the long version, I dump him for telling people the short version.
yingyinNormal.zh: 复杂的说，我因为他说话太简单而甩了他。

yingyinNormal.en: For this modern version, I'm only adding some ale for flavor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在做的这个面包，我只加一点啤酒来提味。

yingyinNormal.en: I like that version as much as the next girl does, believe me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢下面这个的女孩处理的方式，相信我。

yingyinNormal.en: Is Luke doing the Dunphy Tuck? Sort of a poor man's version of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卢克是在做邓菲翻转吗？学了个百分之六七十吧。

yingyinNormal.en: The Leg office predicts the Senate version will pass in two to three weeks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 立法办公室预测参议院法案将在两三周内通过。

yingyinNormal.en: The first street-food dish, my version of egg fu yung, or savoury egg roll.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一道街头小吃，我改良的芙蓉蛋，也就是咸蛋卷。

yingyinNormal.en: Amy, the comic book store is like my version of the country in Black Panther.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾米，漫画书店对我来说就像《黑豹》里的那个国家。
